---
title: Grilled Sweet Chili Shrimp, Salmon Fillets and Chilled Soba Noodles with Marinated Veggies
description: Chilled soba noodles and crunchy fresh veggies tossed in a savoury-sweet nutty sauce is perfect on a warm summer night! Sweet chili shrimp and salmon get a smoky profile from the grill before topping the noodles and a drizzle of sriracha adds a pleasant mild heat.
